One Year After the Great War:  The Hero's Hometown Variante
Celia:  \F[10]\AA[F]...Haa. When will I say it...

\F[10]\AA[F]It's been a year since I moved to this town.
I've been waiting for the right moment to say something very
important in my life.

\F[3]\AA[F]He is Hayato. Since I came to town, he's been
kinder to me than anyone else... a close friend.

\F\c\AA[F]\c[14]This town itself is my birthplace\c[0].
But.. for me, who had moved to the city since I was
conscious, it was an unfamiliar land.

\F[1]\AA[F]It's been over a decade since I returned here due
to the monster invasion in the city... Thanks to Hayato's
support, I was able to quickly adapt to life in Variante.

\F\c[14]\AA[F]Even though he \c[14]lost his older brother in

time...
